   mu g m(-3). The mean concentration of total BTX was maximum during
   winter (393 mu g m(-3)), followed by summer (28.4 mu g m(-) (3)) and
   monsoon season (25.1 mu g m(-3)). The mean concentration of BD( at urban
   site (11.8 mu g m(-3)) was higher than that at rural site (8.8 mu g
   m(-3)). At both the sites, TSB and X/B ratios were highest in monsoon
