   Ablekim, Abdimijit and Zhang, Luocheng},
Title = {{Desert riparian forest colonization in the lower reaches of Tarim River
   based on remote sensing analysis}},
Journal = {{ENVIRONMENTAL EARTH SCIENCES}},
