   the highest number of days on which counts exceeded the threshold levels
   required to trigger allergy symptoms (Sevilla 38 \% and M,rida 30 \% of
   days). Analysis of annual spore distribution patterns revealed either
   one or two peaks, depending on the location and prevailing climate of
   sampling stations. For all stations, average temperature was the weather
