   economic aspects. These models would then be used to verify the
   feasibility of ecological motivated land use claims. The results would
   form the basis for political decision making by a society. The model of
   Meyer-Aurich and Zander {[}Consideration of biotic environmental quality
   targets in agricultural land use-a case study from the biosphere reserve
   Schorfheide-Chorin. In: Buechs, W (Ed.), Biotic Indicators for
